{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then came the announcement about the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The Germans came into Lodz in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It, it couldn't have been very much later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was in the winter, because I remember the snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I remember when we left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had a restricted area that was in a, in a section of town called Baluty.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "B-A-L-U-T-Y.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Baluty.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Predominantly very poor Jewish section of town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Huge section.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was like a whole city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they told us how much time we have until we have to clear the town, and we're not allowed to get in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then they put the wires up and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This couldn't have been later than January, December, January.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "December '39 and January 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I'm not sure about the date, but it had to have been around that time because it was still winter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first few weeks, I think we went to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right after, things started to normalize a little bit after the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the classes weren't normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of the teachers were missing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They left town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because I remember, we were learning to write the Gothic German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "German was the first, one of the first lessons we had to learn that was in the curriculum.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was, I think, the number-one subject was German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this-- when I went into-- in 1939, I went into the last grade of elementary, seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was already messed up, which in-- actually, I didn't properly finish seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then in the ghetto, we had school, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
